<SLUG> BC-FUELCELL-AZR </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
FUEL CELL MAY BEAT BATTERY BLUES 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 BY JONATHAN SIDENER  
