<P>
   COXNET ENTERTAINMENT 0120 _ The Sundance Film Festival, Robert
Redford's annual 10-day fete of independent movies in Park City,
Utah, ushers in the new century of behind-the-scenes dealmaking,
front-and-center celebrity preening and sheer movie fan mania
that's marked the festival for 21 years. (Longino, Atlanta Journal
Constitution) Art includes 4-column color photo from the film
``American Psycho,'' a 2-column color photo from the film ``Happy,
Texas,'' and a 1-column color photo from ``The Blair Witch
Project.''
