projects that U.S. lawmakers supported last year. State-by-state
listing, to be released Thursday, will show the total amount each
member voted in federal subsidies for these programs. Also, the
alliance picked new targets to try to sink this year, including
federal subsidies to dredge Georgia's Savannah Harbor, subsidized
crop insurance, and road paving through national forests. (Malone,
Cox News Service). 25.
