<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    CLINTON, ARAFAT REMAIN CONFIDENT IN PEACE PROCESS, DESPITE
UNCERTAINTY OF MID-FEBRUARY DEADLINE
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (w) Washington categories.
 &HT;    By BOB DEANS 
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service 
