   BRADLEY-IOWA (Des Moines, Iowa) _ Behind in the polls in advance
of the Iowa caucuses, former Sen. Bill Bradley says he is
``upbeat'' about his chances despite being up against the
``entrenched power'' of the Iowa Democratic Party and organized
labor, most of which is supporting Vice President Al Gore. Bradley
campaigns among senior citizens, an important voting segment in a
