<P>
   SAFRICA-EDUCATION (Orange Farm, South Africa) _ Orange Farm,
poor area outside Johannesburg, has emerged as an unlikely model
for South Africa's educational reform. The district emphasizes
disclipine and more stringent rote education than others. By Kurt
Shillingher. 1250 words.
</P>
