100,000 elementary and secondary school teachers integrate
computers and the Internet into their classrooms.
</P>
<P>
   Global Trade Group to Meet in Tokyo
</P>
<P>
   Currency exchange rates are likely to be a contentious issue
when ministers from the Group of Seven industrialized nations meet
this weekend in Tokyo.
</P>
