Price as tested: $59,165 &QL; 
Horsepower/Torque: 275/295 lb-ft. &QL; 
Wheelbase/Overall length: 189.4 inches &QL; 
Width/Height: 70.8 inches/56.7 inches &QL; 
Curb weight: 3,650 lbs. &QL; 
Seating: 5 passengers &QL; 
SOURCE: Manufacturer
</P>
